{
 "name": "RPlog_Meet_Shenner",
 "title": "Meet Shenner",
 "summary": "Aboard a New Republic fleet vessel, the Jedi Jessalyn Valios enters the crew quarters and finds a wary red-haired youngster, Shenner, clutching a guitar case. Shenner, recently spirited off-planet by Luke Skywalker to escape some danger, is skittish and unsure whether the ship belongs to Rebels or Imperials. Through patient, maternal kindness Jessalyn coaxes the frightened kid into conversation, confirming that Luke is safe and that Shenner inadvertently helped him during a fight. She reassures Shenner of safety aboard and urges rest, while a tiger-like Horansi crewmate, the NRI captain Razi, wakes nearby and good-naturedly welcomes their nervous new guest.",
